    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>This staff of magically hardened wood is topped with a silver sculpture depicting magical runic symbols. When used as a weapon, a staff of power is a +2 greater striking staff.<br></span></p>\n<p><span>Voluntarily destroying a staff of power unleashes an incredible blast of energy. When wielding the staff, you can Interact to break it. This releases a 30-foot-burst magical explosion centered on the staff. This deals 2d8 force damage per charge remaining in the staff (DC 40 basic Reflex save). You automatically critically fail your save. A creature reduced to 0 Hit Points by this damage dies instantly; this is a death effect.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell; <strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.J7Y7tl0bbdz7TcCc]{Ray of Enfeeblement} </li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.ynm8JIU3sc3qUMpa]{Continual Flame}</li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.fI20AVwOzJMHXRdo]{Levitate}</li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.JOdOpbPDl7nqvJUm]{Globe of Invulnerability}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.DCQHaLrYXMI37dvW]{Paralyze}</li>\n<li><strong>5th </strong>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.gKKqvLohtrSJj3BM]{Magic Missile}</li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.7Iela4GgVeO3LfAo]{Wall of Force}</li>\n<li><strong>7th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.3puDanGfpEt6jK5k]{Cone of Cold}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.sxQZ6yqTn0czJxVd]{Fireball}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.9AAkVUCwF6WVNNY2]{Lightning Bolt} </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>",
